Ian Gavan, Getty Images Mismatched gloves and a thigh cutout was on fashion house TOGA's catwalk. Niklas Halle'n, AFP/Getty Images A model wears a glitzy pair of sunglasses for the Mulberry show. Daniel Leal-Olivas, AFP/Getty Images This Mulberry model's garment has an atypical hemline. Daniel Leal-Olivas, AFP/Getty Images For Preen by Thornton Bregazzi, a model looked as though she were wearing a comforter. Niklas Halle'n, AFP/Getty Images Preen by Thornton Bregazzi showed plenty of very floral designs. Niklas Halle'n, AFP/Getty Images The Anya Hindmarch show had white wigs and unusually-placed fur.
